{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9241,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「サイアスさん、ですか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Saius-san, is it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9242,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そう、サイアス・クラウンさん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, Saius Crown-san."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9243,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ゼスの炎軍の将軍さんです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He is a general of Zeth’s Flame Army.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9244,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「炎軍ていうと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Flame Army, you say…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9245,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ゼスにある四つの軍隊のうちの一つです。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s one of the four armies in Zeth."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9246,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そこの、一番えらい人ですよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He’s the top-ranking person there.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9247,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はーー……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haa…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9248,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「貴族の出だけれど、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"He’s from a noble family, but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9249,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一兵卒から将軍まで上がったそうですよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I heard he rose from a foot soldier to a general.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9250,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふわぁ……すごい人なんですねえ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wow… he’s an amazing person…"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9251,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　かっこいいし……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And so cool…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9252,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"............\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9253,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そっか。ランスさんが嫌いそうな人ですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I see. He’s probably someone Lance would dislike.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9254,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あはは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, ahaha…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9255,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"............\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9256,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス城の庭の裏手。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Behind the garden of Lance’s castle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9257,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスは、一人の女性ゼス士官と向き合っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saius was facing a female Zeth officer alone."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9258,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だめ、ですか…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Is it no good...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9259,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "女性は緊張と興奮とそれ以外の何かで、震えていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The woman was trembling from nervousness, excitement, and something else."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9260,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "男の真摯な、しかし誤解しようのない拒絶に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "By the man's sincere yet unmistakable rejection,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9261,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "打ちのめされていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She was crushed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9262,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だがサイアスの表情はそれ以上に硬く重く、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "However, Saius’s expression was even harder and heavier,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9263,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "どこか沈痛でさえあった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Somber, even painful, in some way."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9264,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ごめん。俺は、君とは付き合えない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Sorry. I can’t be with you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9265,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぁ、っ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah…!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9266,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「君は、優秀な部下だ。いつも助けてもらってる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You are an excellent subordinate. You always help me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9267,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　でも……すまない。……好きな女がいるんだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But… sorry. There is a woman I like.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9268,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「っ、わか、わかって、ました……っ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I-I understood, I understood…"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9269,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　でも、でも、せめてっ……つたえ、たくてっ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But, but at least… I wanted to tell you…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9270,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ……ありがとう。嬉しいよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah… thank you. That makes me happy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9271,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　……本当に、そう思ってる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "…I really mean that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9272,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「っ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"…!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9273,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "女性は耐えきれなくなり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The woman could not bear it any longer,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9274,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "身を翻して駆け去っていった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She turned around and ran away."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9275,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………ふぅ……けっこうきついな、こりゃ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Phew... this is pretty tough, huh...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9276,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "収まりの悪い髪を掻き、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He scratched his unruly hair,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9277,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスはひとつ、溜息をついた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and sighed once, Saius did."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9278,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「見〜〜〜〜た〜〜〜ぞ〜〜〜〜」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I saw it~~~~!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9279,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おわっ！　…………なんだボーヤか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Whoa! ...Oh, it’s just you, boy.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9280,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "城の物陰から、ランスが現れた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Lance appeared from the shadows of the castle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9281,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「女の子を振ってたのか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You were rejecting a girl, huh."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9282,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もったいない、けっこう可愛かったぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What a waste, she was pretty cute.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9283,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ……まったく同感だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah... I completely agree.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9284,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスは少し表情に影を落としつつ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saius slightly darkened his expression,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9285,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "肩を竦めて苦笑した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "shrugged his shoulders and gave a bitter smile."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9286,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いつもならやんわり、時間をかけて……と、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Usually, I’d gently, over time..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9287,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　傷つけないようにしていたんだがね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I would try not to hurt her."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9288,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちょっと宗旨替え、って奴さ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But I’ve had a bit of a change in approach.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9289,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ムカつく物言いだ……宗旨替え？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That’s an irritating way to put it... A 'change in approach'?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9290,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「世の中の状況が状況だからな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Because the situation in the world is what it is."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9291,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　流石に、人生最後になるかも知れない恋を、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Surely, a love that might be your last in life,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9292,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　応える気のない男に向けるんじゃ不幸だろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "would be unhappy if directed at a man who has no intention of reciprocating.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9293,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「のんびりゆっくり、今日できることを明日やる……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Taking it easy and slowly, doing today’s tasks tomorrow..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9294,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんて余裕は、もう無いからな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We don’t have that luxury anymore.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9295,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（俺自身だって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Even I myself,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9296,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうなるかはまるで分からないしな……）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "have no idea what will happen...)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9297,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーん……変な所で真面目な奴。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... You’re serious in a strange way."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9298,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あの子、お前の部下なのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That girl is your subordinate?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9299,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん？　ああ。今回の随行員だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hm? Yeah. She’s part of my entourage this time."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9300,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　世界がこんなだから、躊躇してられない、ってのは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Because the world is like this, there’s no time to hesitate,"
    }
  ]
}

